    "agent_id_visibility": "diagnostic_only",
    "rule": "Use role_key for stable programmatic routing, display_name for UI/chat labels, and agent_id only for same-task continuation/debug evidence. At new formal startup, agent_id must be fresh for the current task and must not come from prior-route role-binding ledgers or older role-memory packets."
